            <p class="description">Now a VP, my ‚Äúfirst team‚Äù was leadership, and my role was to explore, communicate and negotiate what I believed the longer view of the product should be. A practice I found immensely challenging and rewarding. Over time I found my rhythm with it. To create artefacts that inspired teams, increased clarity, and created options for the future, without derailing focus on the near term goals.</p>
        </div>
